务器的每一个请求，打上「这个人是中国用户」的隐形标记，传回 Anthropic 的服务器。昨天看到社区上 LinXiaoTao 开发了个一键检测功能，挺好用的，将这个功能集成到了 Uwarp</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.uwarp.design/fuck-claude\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fuck Claude 一键检测</a></p>\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.v2ex.co/BYIWi1QN.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1783134549, "replies": 46, "id": 1224898}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 30829, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 3325, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 406395, "username": "xxw1754352621", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xxw1754352621", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_mini.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_normal.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_large.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xlarge.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xxlarge.png?m=1773115604", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f9cb/9fdb/406395_xxxlarge.png?m=1773115604", "created": 1556249871, "last_modified": 1773115604, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "shawnhuang", "last_touched": 1783145614, "title": "因为帮朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus，我的 Apple ID 不干净了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224834", "created": 1783078610, "deleted": 0, "content": "起因是前几个月，我用我的美区 Apple Id ，帮我朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus ，后面这个订阅过期了。\r\n\r\n后来我朋友用自己注册的美区 Apple Id 给自己的 ChatGPT 充值了。\r\n\r\n我最近由于工作需要使用 Codex ，准备自己充一波，钱扣了，然后提示什么错误，发现没有充上。\r\n\r\n点击恢复购买，提示 “你的 AppleID 购买项目关联到另一个 ChatGPT 账号。巴拉巴拉...”。\r\n\r\n后面跟我朋友联系，发现充到他的账号上了。并且是覆盖式的，他在 6 月 30 号充值的，我今天 7 月 3 号 充值的。他的 ChatGPT 账号显示 8 月 3 号过期...\r\n\r\n后来翻阅相关文档，发现是永久绑定的，天塌了！这个美区 Apple ID 是我长期使用的...以前真不知道，还有这样的操作", "content_rendered": "<p>起因是前几个月，我用我的美区 Apple Id ，帮我朋友代充了 ChatGPT Plus ，后面这个订阅过期了。</p>\n<p>后来我朋友用自己注册的美区 Apple Id 给自己的 ChatGPT 充值了。</p>\n<p>我最近由于工作需要使用 Codex ，准备自己充一波，钱扣了，然后提示什么错误，发现没有充上。</p>\n<p>点击恢复购买，提示 “你的 AppleID 购买项目关联到另一个 ChatGPT 账号。巴拉巴拉...”。</p>\n<p>后面跟我朋友联系，发现充到他的账号上了。并且是覆盖式的，他在 6 月 30 号充值的，我今天 7 月 3 号 充值的。他的 ChatGPT 账号显示 8 月 3 号过期...</p>\n<p>后来翻阅相关文档，发现是永久绑定的，天塌了！这个美区 Apple ID 是我长期使用的...以前真不知道，还有这样的操作</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783078610, "replies": 37, "id": 1224834}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_large.png?m=1706750053", "name": "taste", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_normal.png?m=1706750053", "title": "美酒与美食", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/taste", "topics": 874, "footer": "", "header": "关于那些好喝和好吃的", "title_alternative": "Taste", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/735b/90b4/67_mini.png?m=1706750053", "stars": 843, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 67, "parent_node_name": "life"}, "member": {"id": 554904, "username": "11000111010", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/11000111010", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2849eb464101d4e008226d658410ce10?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1630486935, "last_modified": 1753324501, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "sherryspaopao", "last_touched": 1783117468, "title": "咸粽子好吃还是甜粽子好吃？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224812", "created": 1783071150, "deleted": 0, "content": "本人经常吃甜粽子，感觉甜粽子好吃，但是上一个端午节 朋友从南方寄过来几个咸粽子，有叉烧肉咸蛋黄的，有腊肉的还有一个是包的鲜肉粽。感觉都能接受呢？（把币扔给我🤣）", "content_rendered": "本人经常吃甜粽子，感觉甜粽子好吃，但是上一个端午节 朋友从南方寄过来几个咸粽子，有叉烧肉咸蛋黄的，有腊肉的还有一个是包的鲜肉粽。感觉都能接受呢？（把币扔给我🤣）", "last_modified": 1783128791, "replies": 36, "id": 1224812}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11173, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2379, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 410741, "username": "loving29cn", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/loving29cn", "website": "https://www.lajiaohttp.com?kwd=hyj-v2ex", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_mini.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_normal.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_large.png?m=1782264977", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ab4/388e/410741_xlarge.png?m=1782264977", "created": 1557396422, "last_modified": 1782264977, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "copperDC", "last_touched": 1783112815, "title": "求一个好用的蓝牙耳机推荐", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224791", "created": 1783068136, "deleted": 0, "content": "来个不要那么贵的，便宜一点的，质量还可以的，没有运动什么的需求，就平时听听歌，没有噪音，不会断连就行，续航差不多就行，我丢的就剩充电舱了，有线耳机又很容易缠绕，求一个大家用的趁手的", "content_rendered": "<p>来个不要那么贵的，便宜一点的，质量还可以的，没有运动什么的需求，就平时听听歌，没有噪音，不会断连就行，续航差不多就行，我丢的就剩充电舱了，有线耳机又很容易缠绕，求一个大家用的趁手的</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783068136, "replies": 33, "id": 1224791}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/39e4/973b/1248_large.png?m=1782710839", "name": "isv", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/39e4/973b/1248_normal.png?m=1782710839", "title": "独立开发者 👨‍💻", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/isv", "topics": 68, "footer": "独立开发者节点右侧广告位为公益广告位, 免费开放给独立开发者申请", "header": "独立软件开发商(Independent Software Vendors)\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n这里旨在给开发者们提供一个相对聚焦的知识板块.\r\n\r\n愿每一位独立开发者都能保持初心, 都能获得一个好的结果.", "title_alternative": "独立开发者 👨‍💻", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/39e4/973b/1248_mini.png?m=1782710839", "stars": 220, "founder_id": 531733, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 1248, "parent_node_name": null}, "member": {"id": 660606, "username": "RmondJone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/RmondJone", "website": "https://rmondjone.github.io/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "失业码农 家里蹲煮夫", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1617/0aed/660606_mini.png?m=1779171096", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1617/0aed/660606_normal.png?m=1779171096", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1617/0aed/660606_large.png?m=1779171096", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1617/0aed/660606_xlarge.png?m=1779171096", "created": 1699195326, "last_modified": 1779171096, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "NetworkManager", "last_touched": 1783150196, "title": "问大佬们个问题， App 只要接了手机验证码就需要办理等保二级？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224876", "created": 1783123239, "deleted": 0, "content": "今天抖音上面刷到一个哥们，被网安叫到派出所交了 5 万的罚款，就因为他上架的 App 没有做等保。他说他只收集了用户的手机号，只有十几个用户，就被要求做等保三级，这是什么规定？有了解的老哥出来说说?查了下还挺贵的，二级是每年 2 万，三级是每年 5 万。\r\n\r\n这样搞国内市场看来真的得放弃了，还没有什么成果呢，上来就要交钱，不交钱就得吃罚款！", "content_rendered": "<p>今天抖音上面刷到一个哥们，被网安叫到派出所交了 5 万的罚款，就因为他上架的 App 没有做等保。他说他只收集了用户的手机号，只有十几个用户，就被要求做等保三级，这是什么规定？有了解的老哥出来说说?查了下还挺贵的，二级是每年 2 万，三级是每年 5 万。</p>\n<p>这样搞国内市场看来真的得放弃了，还没有什么成果呢，上来就要交钱，不交钱就得吃罚款！</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783123239, "replies": 28, "id": 1224876}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1733731195", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1733731195", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 71872, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1733731195", "stars": 9720, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 235515, "username": "fansmaster", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/fansmaster", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_mini.png?m=1742437032", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_normal.png?m=1742437032", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a657/bc40/235515_large.png?m=1742437032", "created": 1497432809, "last_modified": 1742437032, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "TIDS", "last_touched": 1783097787, "title": "做海外模型的 API 中转站，会被判刑吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224797", "created": 1783068870, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00\r\n\r\n看了这个新闻，感觉有点虚啊，别钱没赚到，人进去了，有没有比较了解相关法律的给说说", "content_rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260629A07O8W00</a></p>\n<p>看了这个新闻，感觉有点虚啊，别钱没赚到，人进去了，有没有比较了解相关法律的给说说</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783068870, "replies": 26, "id": 1224797}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23754, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3705, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 503692, "username": "rimworld", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/rimworld", "website": "https://www.duyihao.com", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "mutuyihao", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_mini.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_normal.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_large.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_xlarge.png?m=1781236811", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a8eb/0af2/503692_xxlarge.png?m=1781236811", "created": 1597330016, "last_modified": 1781236811, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "konakona", "last_touched": 1783104333, "title": "多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML 的那个遥远的下午", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1224814", "created": 1783071691, "deleted": 0, "content": "哎，工作好难找。\r\n打了几千个招呼，就个位数约面，然后走不到终面就没消息了。\r\n最近这家更是不做人了，HR 好友都加不上，面完一周也没消息。在线面试面试官也不开摄像头。\r\n多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML ，听着电脑机箱风扇的噪音，吹着风扇，室友在上铺打着农药的那个遥远的下午。", "content_rendered": "哎，工作好难找。<br />打了几千个招呼，就个位数约面，然后走不到终面就没消息了。<br />最近这家更是不做人了，HR 好友都加不上，面完一周也没消息。在线面试面试官也不开摄像头。<br />多年以后，面对前端如此困难的求职环境，你是否还会回想起当初第一次敲下 HTML ，听着电脑机箱风扇的噪音，吹着风扇，室友在上铺打着农药的那个遥远的下午。", "last_modified": 1783071691, "replies": 26, "id": 1224814}]